data.description: Move-in-ready! Natural light abounds in the open great room with vaulted ceilings and gas fireplace. Bay windows frame beautiful views across the valley to the western mountains. Island kitchen with gas cooktop. Convection wall oven. Huge walk-in pantry. Spacious cabinets & granite countertops. Large dining area and sunny breakfast nook open onto over-size backyard and covered patio. Enjoy the waterfall, firepit, gazebo and beautiful landscaping with fruit trees in this private park-like setting. Large master suite with dual vanities and walk-in closets, separated by a soaking tub and large shower. Smart home tech features. Paved, gated RV parking with hookups. Room for large toys, and an oversized garage with plenty of height for a lift. Beautiful well-maintained home with obvious pride-of-ownership! Schedule your showing today!
